2011年7月1日，[[密歇根州|密歇根州]][[美国众议院|联邦众议员]][[撒迪厄斯·麦科特尔|撒迪厄斯·麦科特尔]]向[[联邦选举委员会|联邦选举委员会]]递交文件，宣布自己有意争夺[[2012年美国总统选举|2012年大选]]的[[共和党_(美国)|共和党]][[美国总统|总统]]候选人提名。一周后，他在[[底特律|底特律]]附近举行的摇滚音乐节上正式宣布参选。

麦科特尔自2003年开始在[[美国国会|国会]]任职，2011年4月，[[福克斯新闻频道|福克斯新闻频道]]的《红眼》节目第一个询问他是否有意竞选总统。两个多月后，麦科特尔的竞选网站上线，其上以他2011年出版的书籍名称《把握自由！》为口号，并列出“5项核心原则”。竞选期间，他强调改革政府和[[华尔街|华尔街]]。

多位评论员指出，麦科特尔欠缺知名度，因此获得提名的希望渺茫。即便是到了2012年美国总统共和党初选全国民意调查时，他的支持率仍然不足1%。由于在埃姆斯民意调查中排名垫底，且没有收到任何总统辩论邀请，麦科特尔于2011年9月22日放弃竞争，表示支持[[米特·罗姆尼|米特·罗姆尼]]。他有意竞选连任国会议员，却陷身选票欺诈案，最终于2012年7月从国会辞职，有4名助手被法院定罪。为了走出竞选失败的阴影，麦科特尔在车库中写出一部[[电视试播|电视试播]]剧本，但尚未完成就被泄露给媒体，对他的名声造成进一步损害。

== 背景 ==
1993年，[[撒迪厄斯·麦科特尔|撒迪厄斯·麦科特尔]]入选[[韦恩县_(密歇根州)|韦恩县]]委员会，拉开从政生涯序幕。5年后，他当选[[密歇根州参议院|密歇根州参议员]]，<ref name="congress">{{cite web | url = http://congress.org/bio/id/851 | title = Rep. Thaddeus McCotter (R-MI 11th District) | year = 2011 | publisher = Congress.org | accessdate = 2011-08-10 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110810224042/http://www.congress.org/bio/id/851 | archivedate = 2011-08-10 }}</ref>并任职至2002年当选[[密歇根州第十一国会选区|密歇根州第十一国会选区]][[美国众议院|联邦众议员]]为止<ref name="congress" />。
[[File:Thaddeus_McCotter,_official_portrait,_112th_Congress.jpg|thumb]]

进入国会后，麦科特尔被派入[[美国众议院金融服务委员会|众议院金融服务委员会]]任职，他还加入了立场较为温和的[[共和党主流社团|共和党主流社团]]<ref>{{cite web | url = http://iowaindependent.com/58080/little-known-mccotter-makes-2012-run-official | title = Little known McCotter makes 2012 run official | last = Malloy | first = Meghan | date = 2011-07-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120929001818/http://iowaindependent.com/58080/little-known-mccotter-makes-2012-run-official/ | work = The Iowa Independent | accessdate = 2012-09-29 | archivedate = 2012-09-29 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。2006年，他成为[[美国众议院指导与政策委员会|众议院共和党政策委员会]]主席，两年后出任共和党财务诚实工作组组长。在该组工作期间，他赢得了[[政治分肥|政治分肥]]头号反对者的良好声誉<ref>{{cite news | title = Thaddeus McCotter (R-Mich.) | year = 2010 | work = The Washington Post}}</ref>。他投票反对《[[经济稳定紧急法案|经济稳定紧急法案]]》和《[[美国可负担卫生保健法案|2010年美国可负担卫生保健法案]]》<ref>{{cite web | url = http://votesmart.org/candidate/key-votes/19847/thaddeus-mccotter | title = Thaddeus McCotter's Voting Records | publisher = Project Vote Smart | accessdate = 2015-02-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130603190745/https://votesmart.org/candidate/key-votes/19847/thaddeus-mccotter | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-06-03 }}</ref>，但对2009年汽车工业危机的[[2008至2010年汽车工业危机对美国的影响|救市政策]]投了赞成票。他还支持提升[[最低工资|最低工资]]，主张同[[中华人民共和国|中华人民共和国]]进行[[公平贸易|公平贸易]]。虽然有这些相对开明的立场，但《[[底特律自由新闻报|底特律自由新闻报]]》（{{lang|en|''Detroit Free Press''}}）仍然称他是“保守派中的保守派”<ref>{{cite news | work = Detroit Free Press | date = 2011-07-11 | last = Spangler | first = Todd | title = Thad McCotter's White House bid: A long shot to keep an eye on}}</ref>，{{lang|en|GovTrack}}网站还给他贴上了“极右翼共和党人”的标签<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141008034212/https://www.govtrack.us/congress/members/thaddeus_mccotter/400260 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.govtrack.us/congress/members/thaddeus_mccotter/400260 | title = Rep. Thaddeus “Thad” McCotter | publisher = GovTrack | accessdate = 2015-02-28 | archivedate = 2014-10-08 | quote = McCotter was a far-right Republican according to GovTrack's own analysis of bill sponsorship from McCotter’s time serving in the House of Representatives. }}</ref>。

在其他国会议员眼中，麦科特尔性格古怪，表现出的幽默感也很扭曲，贝特西·伍德拉夫（{{lang|en|Betsy Woodruff}}）在《[[国家评论|国家评论]]》（{{lang|en|''National Review''}}）杂志上称他是“最奇怪的国会议员”<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140814220757/http://www.nationalreview.com/articles/322406/strangest-congressman-betsy-woodruff | url = http://www.nationalreview.com/articles/322406/strangest-congressman-betsy-woodruff | title = The Strangest Congressman | last = Woodruff | first = Betsy | date = 2012-09-19 | work = National Review | accessdate = 2014-08-14 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-08-14 }}</ref>。他钟爱[[摇滚乐|摇滚乐]]，是“第二修正案”（{{lang|en|Second Amendments}}）乐队的首席[[吉他|吉他]]手<ref name="po">{{cite web | url = http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0511/55546.html | title = Thaddeus McCotter weighing White House bid | last = Martin | first = Jonathan | date = 2011-05-24 | work = Politico | accessdate = 2015-02-28 | archivedate = 2014-05-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140528033902/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0511/55546.html }}</ref>，在众议院讲话时还会援引[[齐柏林飞船_(乐团)|齐柏林飞船]]的歌词<ref name="re" />。[[美国总统|总统]][[乔治·沃克·布什|乔治·沃克·布什]]曾形容麦科特尔是“那个摇哥滚爷”<ref name="po" />。此外，麦科特尔经常现身[[福克斯新闻频道|福克斯新闻频道]]的深夜和早间节目《[[红眼_(电视节目)|红眼]]》（{{lang|en|''Red Eye w/ Greg Gutfeld''}}）。据《每日来电》（{{lang|en|''The Daily Caller''}}）的马特·刘易斯（{{lang|en|Matt Lewis}}）所说，麦科特尔属“红眼候选人”，喜欢摇滚乐，代表的是有“创造性思维”、且倾向于[[自由意志主义|自由意志主义]]的共和党人亚文化<ref name="re">{{cite web | url = http://dailycaller.com/2011/05/24/the-red-eye-candidate/ | title = The Red Eye candidate? | last = Lewis | first = Matt | date = 2011-05-24 | work = The Daily Caller | accessdate = 2015-02-28 | archivedate = 2014-05-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140527213256/http://dailycaller.com/2011/05/24/the-red-eye-candidate/ }}</ref>。《[[彭博商业周刊|彭博商业周刊]]》称他“狂热追随过分忧虑的保守派人士”<ref name="bb">{{cite web | archivedate = 2012-06-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120602033500/http://www.businessweek.com/articles/2012-05-31/run-for-president-kill-your-career | url = http://www.bloomberg.com/bw/articles/2012-05-31/run-for-president-kill-your-career | title = Run for President, Kill Your Career | last = Green | first = Joshua | author2 = Elizabeth Dwoskin | date = 2012-05-31 | work = Bloomberg Businessweek | accessdate = 2015-02-28 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

== 前期炒作 ==
[[File:Thad_McCotter.jpg|thumb]]上演讲。]]

2011年2月，麦科特尔所著的《把握自由！混乱时代中的美国真理和复兴》（{{lang|en|''Seize Freedom! American Truths and Renewal in a Chaotic Age''}}）一书发行。4月22日，《红眼》节目[[主持人|主持人]][[格雷格·盖特菲德|格雷格·盖特菲德]]（{{lang|en|Greg Gutfeld}}）询问麦科特尔，是否有意参选总统<ref>{{cite web | accessdate = 2015-02-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121011004817/http://video.foxnews.com/v/4657219/gutfeld-thaddeus-mccotter-should-run-for-president/ | url = http://video.foxnews.com/v/4657219/gutfeld-thaddeus-mccotter-should-run-for-president/ | title = Gutfeld: Thaddeus McCotter Should Run for President | date = 2011-04-22 | publisher = Fox News | archivedate = 2012-10-11 }}</ref>。5天后，同为《红眼》常客的政治评论员[[莎拉·伊丽莎白·卡普|莎拉·伊丽莎白·卡普]]（{{lang|en|Sarah Elizabeth "S. E." Cupp}}）在自己主持的《[[紐約每日新聞|每日新闻]]》专栏中将麦科特尔列为潜在总统[[候选人|候选人]]<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150216194104/http://www.nydailynews.com/opinion/thaddeus-mccotter-guitar-hero-2012-dark-horse-michigan-star-rises-washington-article-1.113170 | last = Cupp | first = S.E. | archivedate = 2015-02-16 | url = http://www.nydailynews.com/opinion/thaddeus-mccotter-guitar-hero-2012-dark-horse-michigan-star-rises-washington-article-1.113170 | title = Thaddeus McCotter, guitar hero and 2012 dark horse: A Michigan star rises in Washington | date = 2011-04-27 | work = Daily News | accessdate = 2015-02-28 }}</ref>。麦科特尔于5月确认，他的确在认真考虑参选。他在接受《[[政治_(杂志)|政治]]》（{{lang|en|''Politico''}}）杂志采访时表示，自己觉得大部分共和党人对现阶段参选缺乏积极性。评论员[[安德鲁·布赖特巴特|安德鲁·布赖特巴特]]（{{lang|en|Andrew Breitbart}}）表示对麦科特尔的竞选前景感到激动，称他“直截了当、尖酸刻薄，精通流行文化，充满活力言辞真实可信”，自己对麦科特尔参与的辩论最为期待。<ref name="po" />

2011年5月，麦科特尔在共和党领袖人物[[米特·罗姆尼|米特·罗姆尼]]到访底特律期间展开攻势，他将罗姆尼与在任总统[[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]联系起来，声称人们应当把两人视为竞选搭档而非对手<ref>{{cite news | title = McCotter bashes Romney for anti-auto sentiments | work = The Detroit News | date = 2011-06-09 | last = Hurst | first = Nathan}}</ref>。同月下旬，他在[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]举行的南方共和党领袖大会上演说，他的名字也列入大会[[民意测验|民意测验]]考虑名单，但在共计1542票中只得到2票，是得票数最少的人选<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rlc2011.com/rlc/rlc-2011-straw-poll-results/ | title = RLC 2011 Straw Poll Results | publisher = Republican Leadership Conference 2011 | accessdate = 2015-02-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140418202925/http://www.rlc2011.com/rlc/rlc-2011-straw-poll-results/ | archivedate = 2014-04-18 }}</ref><ref name="det">{{cite news | title = McCotter making 2012 presidential bid | last = Shepardson | first = David | author2 = Nathan Hurst | date = 2011-07-01 | work = The Detroit News}}</ref>。据他的助手所说，虽然已于8月13日向[[埃姆斯民意调查|埃姆斯民意调查]]支付1.8万美元购买问卷上较为靠前的位置<ref name="det" />，但麦科特尔这个时候还没有真正决定是否参选<ref>{{cite news | title = McCotter representative adds confusion to Iowa straw poll | work = The Detroit News | date = 2011-06-23 | last = Hurst | first = Nathan}}</ref>。[[爱荷华州|爱荷华州]]是第一个针对[[美国总统大选|美国总统大选]]举办[[爱荷华州预选|预选]]的州，到访该州期间，麦科特尔宣布自己会在民意测试开始前透露竞选方案<ref>{{cite news |url=http://caucuses.desmoinesregister.com/2011/06/29/mccotter-hunts-for-support-in-iowa/ |title=McCotter hunts for support in Iowa |work=The Des Moines Register |date=2011-06-29 |accessdate=2015-02-28 |last=Jacobs |first=Jennifer |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20131010050209/http://caucuses.desmoinesregister.com/2011/06/29/mccotter-hunts-for-support-in-iowa/ |archivedate=2013-10-10 }}</ref>。6月30日，《政治》杂志报道称麦科特尔已经做好展开竞选的准备<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0611/58168.html | title = Thaddeus McCotter to file for president Friday | last = Burns | first = Alexander | date = 2011-06-30 | work = Politico | accessdate = 2015-02-28 | archivedate = 2014-09-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140929132612/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0611/58168.html }}</ref>。

== 选战经过 ==
=== 公布 ===
