2011年7月1日，麦科特尔向联邦选举委员会申请组建总统竞选委员会<ref>{{cite web |url=http://images.nictusa.com/cgi-bin/fecimg/?C00498220 |title=McCotter 2012 |publisher=Federal Election Commission |accessdate=2015-02-28 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303214007/http://images.nictusa.com/cgi-bin/fecimg/?C00498220 |archivedate=2016-03-03 }}</ref>，他的竞选网站也于当天上线。网站上警告世人，“你的[[美国梦|美国梦]]已濒临灭绝”，这一说法源自他之前出版的《把握自由！》一书，网站上还列出了以下“5项核心原则”：<ref name="det" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://dailycaller.com/2011/07/01/thaddeus-mccotters-presidential-slogan-seize-freedom/ | title = Thaddeus McCotter's presidential slogan: 'Seize Freedom!' | last = Pappas | first = Alex | date = 2011-07-01 | work = The Daily Caller | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121004040131/http://dailycaller.com/2011/07/01/thaddeus-mccotters-presidential-slogan-seize-freedom/ | archivedate = 2012-10-04 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-02-28 }}</ref>
#“我们的自由来自上帝而非政府”
#“我们的主权属于我们的灵魂而非国土”
#“我们的安全是依靠实力而非投降”
#“我们的繁荣源自私人机构而非公共部门”
#“我们的真理不言而喻而非相对而论”
7月2日，麦科特尔在密歇根州[[沃什特瑙县_(密西根州)|沃什特瑙县]][[惠特莫尔湖_(密歇根州)|惠特莫尔湖]]（{{lang|en|Whitmore Lake}}）举办的“自由节”正式宣布参选，这是一场由{{lang|en|WAAM}}电台赞助的摇滚音乐节。麦科特尔宣称：“我们需要身在[[哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿]]的人明白，未来的潮流不是大政府，而是自治。”<ref name="free">{{cite news | title = McCotter launches White House run at tea party holiday rally | work = Detroit Free Press | date = 2011-07-03 | last = Gray | first = Kathleen}}</ref>他还在音乐节上与自己的摇滚乐队一起表演<ref>{{cite news | title = McCotter Officially Announces White House Run | work = The Wall Street Journal | date = 2011-07-02}}</ref>。得知众议员参选后，《库克政治报道》（{{lang|en|''The Cook Political Report''}}）创始人查理·库克（{{lang|en|Charlie Cook}}）将麦科特尔获得提名的可能性评为“基本上不可能”<ref name="det" />。《[[CBS新闻|CBS新闻]]》及其他媒体认为麦科特尔缺乏知名度，是个“默默无闻”的候选人<ref name="cbs">{{cite web | title = Michigan Rep. Thaddeus McCotter to jump into Republican presidential race | last = Madison | first = Lucy | date = 2011-07-01 | publisher = CBS News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150228153011/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/michigan-rep-thaddeus-mccotter-to-jump-into-republican-presidential-race/ | archivedate = 2015-02-28 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-02-28 | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/michigan-rep-thaddeus-mccotter-to-jump-into-republican-presidential-race/ }}</ref>。不过，《[[底特律自由新闻报|底特律自由新闻报]]》（{{lang|en|''Detroit Free Press''}}）指出，麦科特尔的国会账户中有48万[[美元|美元]]可以转入总统竞选账户<ref name="free" />。政治通讯操盘手[[马克·科拉洛|马克·科拉洛]]（{{lang|en|Mark Corallo}}）获聘成为竞选团队的一员，还有多位顾问成为竞选核心团队成员，如前[[美国参议院|联邦参议员]][[比尔·弗里斯特|比尔·弗里斯特]]（{{lang|en|Bill Frist}}）的幕僚长艾里克·尤兰德（{{lang|en|Eric Uelind}}）、前爱荷华州联邦众议员克里斯托弗·兰茨（{{lang|en|Christopher Rants}}）<ref name="cbs" />。

=== 竞选活动 ===
麦科特尔正式竞选行程的第一站是[[新罕布什尔州|新罕布什尔州]]，该州是全国[[初选|初选]]启动最早的州<ref>{{cite news | title = McCotter launches campaign for GOP presidential nomination | work = The Detroit News | date = 2011-07-03 | last = Schultz | first = Marisa}}</ref>，与此同时，麦科特尔故乡的报纸对他竞选总统的反应引起媒体关注<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.uncoveredpolitics.com/2011/07/08/the-thought-of-mccotter-as-president-a-%E2%80%98bit-scary%E2%80%99-says-michigan-newspaper/ | title = The Thought of McCotter as President a 'Bit Scary,' Says Michigan Newspaper | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150228160712/http://www.uncoveredpolitics.com/2011/07/08/the-thought-of-mccotter-as-president-a-%E2%80%98bit-scary%E2%80%99-says-michigan-newspaper/ | last = Richardson | first = Darcy | date = 2011-07-08 | work = Uncovered Politics | accessdate = 2015-02-28 | archivedate = 2015-02-28 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.politico.com/blogs/bensmith/0711/No_hometown_support_for_McCotter.html | title = No hometown support for McCotter | last = Smith | first = Ben | date = 2011-07-11 | work = Politico | accessdate = 2015-02-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110721012433/http://www.politico.com/blogs/bensmith/0711/No_hometown_support_for_McCotter.html | archivedate = 2011-07-21 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2012-07-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120723091311/http://www.outsidethebeltway.com/thad-mccotters-hometown-newspaper-gives-him-a-bad-review/ | url = http://www.outsidethebeltway.com/thad-mccotters-hometown-newspaper-gives-him-a-bad-review/ | title = Thad McCotter's Hometown Newspaper Gives Him A Bad Review | last = Mataconis | first = Doug | date = 2011-07-11 | work = Outside the Beltway | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。密歇根州[[奥克兰县_(密歇根州)|奥克兰县]]的《奥克兰新闻报》（{{lang|en|''The Oakland Press''}}）在社论中称，让麦科特尔当总统“不是个会让人愉快的想法，事实上还有点吓人”<ref name="scary">{{cite web |archivedate=2013-07-27 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130727023019/http://iowaindependent.com/58372/mccotters-paper-labels-his-2012-bid-as-scary |url=http://iowaindependent.com/58372/mccotters-paper-labels-his-2012-bid-as-scary |title=McCotter's paper labels his 2012 bid as 'scary' |last=Heywood |first=Todd A. |date=2011-07-12 |work=The Iowa Independent |accessdate=2013-07-27 }}</ref>，报道中批评“这位众议员给人的印象冷淡、傲慢而自负”<ref name="scary" />。麦科特尔总体上无视这些批评<ref>{{cite web | title = What Makes Thaddeus McCotter Run? | last = Alberta | first = Tim | date = 2011-07-12 | work = National Journal | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archivedate = 2012-04-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120406061958/http://www.nationaljournal.com/politics/what-makes-thaddeus-mccotter-run--20110712 | url = http://www.nationaljournal.com/politics/what-makes-thaddeus-mccotter-run--20110712 }}</ref>，继续在新罕布什尔州竞选，强调“对政府加以根本性重组”<ref>{{cite news | title = Republican Presidential Hopeful Thaddeus McCotter Visits N.H. | date = 2011-07-11 | publisher = WMUR-TV}}</ref>，并签署[[苏珊·安东尼名单|苏珊·安东尼名单]]的生命权领袖誓言<ref>{{cite web | url = http://detroit.cbslocal.com/2011/07/11/mccotter-takes-pro-life-pledge/ | title = McCotter Takes ‘Pro-Life’ Pledge | date = 2011-07-11 | work = CBS Detroit | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2011-09-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110912151401/http://detroit.cbslocal.com/2011/07/11/mccotter-takes-pro-life-pledge/ }}</ref>。电台主持人克里斯·巴克（{{lang|en|Chris Buck}}）获聘打点麦特科尔在新罕布什尔州的活动<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.uncoveredpolitics.com/2011/07/13/mccotter-appoints-campaign-director-in-new-hampshire/ | title = McCotter Appoints Campaign Director in New Hampshire | last = Richardson | first = Darcy | date = 2011-07-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120328085626/http://www.uncoveredpolitics.com/2011/07/13/mccotter-appoints-campaign-director-in-new-hampshire/ | work = Uncovered Politics | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archivedate = 2012-03-28 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。
[[File:SECupp-MG-1028.jpg|thumb]]}}上举行的辩论。]]

7月中旬，麦科特尔返回爱荷华州展开更多竞选活动<ref>{{cite web |url=http://caucuses.desmoinesregister.com/2011/07/14/presidential-candidate-thaddeus-mccotter-in-iowa-monday/ |title=Presidential candidate Thaddeus McCotter in Iowa Monday |last=Jacobs |first=Jennifer |date=2011-07-14 |work=The Des Moines Register |accessdate=2015-03-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130505095012/http://caucuses.desmoinesregister.com/2011/07/14/presidential-candidate-thaddeus-mccotter-in-iowa-monday/ |archivedate=2013-05-05 }}</ref>。这一期间《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的克里斯·塞利扎（{{lang|en|Chris Cillizza}}）认为，麦科特尔在埃姆斯民意调查中胜出的赔率为100比1，是候选人中希望最渺茫的一位<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2012-republican-presidential-campaign-who-will-iowas-ames-straw-poll-make-break/2011/07/10/gIQAEWDk7H_story.html?wpisrc=emailtoafriend | title = 2012 Republican presidential campaign: Who will Iowa's Ames Straw Poll make, break? | last = Cillizza | first = Chris | date = 2011-07-10 | work = The Washington Post | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archive-date = 2020-08-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200808130137/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2012-republican-presidential-campaign-who-will-iowas-ames-straw-poll-make-break/2011/07/10/gIQAEWDk7H_story.html?wpisrc=emailtoafriend | dead-url = no }}</ref>。7月11至18日进行的[[哈里斯民意调查|哈里斯民意调查]]结果显示，92%的选民对麦科特尔缺乏了解，并且与其他总统候选人相比，愿意支持他的还不到1%。假设麦科特尔与在任总统奥巴马直接竞争，愿意支持麦科特尔的选民有43%，支持奥巴马的则是57%。<ref>{{cite web | location = New York, N.Y. | publisher = Harris Interactive | title = President Obama Would Lose if Mitt Romney or Rudy Giuliani Was the Nominee | date = 2011-07-26 | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120605030053/http://www.harrisinteractive.com/NewsRoom/HarrisPolls/tabid/447/mid/1508/articleId/840/ctl/ReadCustom%20Default/Default.aspx | archivedate = 2012-06-05 | url = http://www.harrisinteractive.com/NewsRoom/HarrisPolls/tabid/447/mid/1508/articleId/840/ctl/ReadCustom%20Default/Default.aspx }}</ref>。为争取支持，麦科特尔试图绕开新闻媒体，直接用{{lang|en|[[Twitter|Twitter]]}}与选民交流。竞选活动发言人兰德尔·汤普森（{{lang|en|Randall Thompson}}）表示，麦科特尔“依靠社交媒体……发展出非常忠实的追随者”。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0711/58531_Page2.html | title = Rep. Thad McCotter finds friends on Hill | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121013190808/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0711/58531_Page2.html | deadurl = no | last = Weinger | first = Mackenzie | author2 = Andy Barr | date = 2011-07-07 | work = Politico | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archivedate = 2012-10-13 }}</ref>

7月20日，麦科特尔参加了[[美国历史|历史]]上首次{{lang|en|Twitter}}总统辩论，他的对手包括[[新墨西哥州|新墨西哥州]]前[[新墨西哥州州长名单|州长]][[加里·约翰逊|加里·约翰逊]]（{{lang|en|Gary Johnson}}）、商人[[赫尔曼·凯恩|赫尔曼·凯恩]]、联邦众议员[[米歇尔·巴赫曼|米歇尔·巴赫曼]]、前[[美国众议院议长|联邦众议院议长]][[纽特·金里奇|纽特·金里奇]]及前联邦参议员[[里克·桑托勒姆|里克·桑托勒姆]]。辩论期间，主持人莎拉·伊丽莎白·卡普询问，奥巴马总统是否有反[[以色列|以色列]]倾向，麦科特尔这样回答：“奥巴马的动机无关紧要，他提出和推行的政策已经导致我们（同以色列）的关系变得紧张。”<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131111224545/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0711/59516.html | archivedate = 2013-11-11 | url = http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0711/59516.html | title = Candidates face off on Twitter | last = Summers | first = Juana | date = 2011-07-20 | work = Politico | accessdate = 2015-03-01 }}</ref>面对[[2011年多国武装干涉利比亚|2011年武装干涉利比亚]]期间美国起到的作用问题，麦科特尔认为奥巴马政府在任务目标上把握不清，主张不派任何美军地面部队参战。不过他又补充道：“一旦加入，我们就不能冒然退出。”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://140townhall.com/ | title = First Presidential Debate on Twitter (Transcript) | date = 2011-07-20 | publisher = 140townhall.com | accessdate = 2011-07-23 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110726201113/http://140townhall.com/ | archivedate = 2011-07-26 }}</ref>

7月下旬正是[[2011年美国债务上限危机|债务上限危机]]的高峰时期，麦科特尔取消在爱荷华州的多场露面活动返回哥伦比亚特区。他支持众议院议长[[约翰·博纳|约翰·博纳]]提出的方案<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-05-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130507033042/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0711/60183.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0711/60183.html | title = Debt ceiling debate causes turmoil for 2012 hopefuls | last = Summers | first = Juana | date = 2011-07-28 | work = Politico | accessdate = 2015-03-01 }}</ref>，并投票赞成[[2011年预算控制法案|折衷法案]]。巴赫曼和[[荣·保罗|荣·保罗]]都投票反对该法案，所以麦科特尔也就成为联邦众议院中唯一赞成法案的总统候选人<ref>{{cite web | url = http://projects.washingtonpost.com/congress/112/house/1/votes/690/ | title = Final debt deal | date = 2011-08-01 | work = The Washington Post | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archive-date = 2019-04-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190416082835/http://projects.washingtonpost.com/congress/112/house/1/votes/690/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。
[[File:Thaddeus_McCotter_by_Gage_Skidmore.jpg|upright]]

埃姆斯民意调查前，麦科特尔的支持率尚不足1%，没有达到参与8月11日在福克斯新闻频道举行辩论的最低要求。即便是在自己的故乡，他的支持率都很低。[[公共政策民调|公共政策民调]]表明，密歇根州支持他的共和党选民仅5%，考虑到这是他的故乡，这样的数字在历史上也可谓凤毛麟角。<ref>{{cite web | title = McCotter has no support with MI GOP, Romney tops field | last = Jensen | first = Tom | date = 2011-08-09 | publisher = Public Policy Polling | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130913003150/http://www.publicpolicypolling.com/main/2011/08/mccotter-has-no-support-with-mi-gop-romney-tops-field.html#more | archivedate = 2013-09-13 | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | url = http://www.publicpolicypolling.com/main/2011/08/mccotter-has-no-support-with-mi-gop-romney-tops-field.html#more }}</ref>得知自己的处境后，麦科特尔取消了原计划在新罕布什尔州的一站竞选活动，返回位于密歇根州的竞选总部配合辩论相关工作<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0811/60919.html | title = Iowa in mind, McCotter drops N.H. Stops | last = Summers | first = Juana | date = 2011-08-08 | work = Politico | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131221035833/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0811/60919.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2013-12-21 }}</ref>。他的竞选团队拍摄了一段{{lang|en|[[YouTube|YouTube]]}}视频，内容是麦科特尔在厨房里使用各种厨具，配合一些语意双关的台词<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2012-07-15 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120715024907/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/aug/05/news/la-pn-mccotter-video-bad-puns-20110805 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2011/aug/05/news/la-pn-mccotter-video-bad-puns-20110805 | title = Bad puns? Check. Standing in the polls? Not yet for GOP presidential hopeful Thaddeus McCotter | last = Goldmacher | first = Shane | date = 2011-08-05 | work = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2015-03-01 }}</ref>。《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》对视频评价不佳，称观看视频令人感到“不幸”<ref name="lat-wd">{{cite news | title = Long-shot GOP hopeful Thaddeus McCotter ends presidential bid | last = Memoli | first = Michael | date = 2011-09-22 | work = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121217053224/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/sep/22/news/la-pn-thaddeus-mccotter-campaign-20110922 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2011/sep/22/news/la-pn-thaddeus-mccotter-campaign-20110922 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-12-17 }}</ref>。虽然做出了这样的努力，但麦科特尔还是因未达门槛而无法参加福克斯新闻频道的辩论，是取得埃姆斯民意调查资格但却无法参加辩论的唯一一位候选人<ref>{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150227194024/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0811/61098.html | archivedate = 2015-02-27 | url = http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0811/61098.html | title = Barred hopefuls make debate plans | last = Summers | first = Juana | date = 2011-08-11 | work = Politico | accessdate = 2015-03-01 }}</ref>。

埃姆斯民意调查开始前，麦科特尔向选民发表演说，《政治》杂志形容，这是场“缓慢、抽象，（表现）分外冷静的演说”<ref name="speech">{{cite news | url = http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0811/61305.html#ixzz1oyZIzx3E | title = Thaddeus McCotter draws cheers with China attack | last = Burns | first = Alexander | date = 2011-08-13 | work = Politico | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120317131902/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/0811/61305.html#ixzz1oyZIzx3E | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archivedate = 2012-03-17 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。除演讲中谴责“北京政权”、宣称“我不会把21世纪拱手让给一个拥有[[核武器|核武器]]的[[共产主义|共产主义]]独裁国家”的说法引来一些掌声外，他的演说没有得到什么反应<ref name="speech" />。麦科特尔花了很多时间待在自己的帐蓬里弹吉他<ref>{{cite news |url=http://caucuses.desmoinesregister.com/2011/08/13/mccotter-finishes-dead-last-with-35-votes/ |title=McCotter finishes dead last, with 35 votes |last=Noble |first=Jason |date=2011-08-13 |work=The Des Moines Register |accessdate=2015-03-01 |archivedate=2012-11-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20121102093641/http://caucuses.desmoinesregister.com/2011/08/13/mccotter-finishes-dead-last-with-35-votes/ }}</ref>，他在民意调查中一共只得到35票，得票率仅0.21%，在10名候选人中垫底<ref name="la" />。考虑到他为选票位置支付了1.8万美元，这相当于平均每票514美元<ref name="la">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130822080153/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/aug/13/news/la-pn-straw-numbers-20110813 | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2011/aug/13/news/la-pn-straw-numbers-20110813 | title = Ames Straw Poll: Final results | last = Oliphant | first = James | date = 2011-08-13 | work = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archivedate = 2013-08-22 }}</ref>。资深顾问克里斯托弗·兰茨表示，参加这场民意调查的目的“不是为了选票，而是在第一个大型论坛向公众介绍我们的候选人……无论如何，我们都做到了这点”<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.p2012.org/iastraw/straw081311rxn.html | title = McCotter Performs Well At Straw Poll (Press Release) | date = 2011-08-13 | work = Democracy in Action | publisher = Eric M. Appleman | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120615014441/http://www.p2012.org/iastraw/straw081311rxn.html | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archivedate = 2012-06-15 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。
