埃姆斯民意调查结束3天后，麦科特尔致信《国家评论》，介绍自己的部分经济计划。他主张削减开支，将银行[[存款准备金比率|存款准备金比率]]定在20%来保留资本，并通过激励机制减少房屋止赎<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121120094225/http://www.politifact.com/truth-o-meter/statements/2011/aug/23/thaddeus-mccotter/thaddeus-mccotter-says-lenders-lose-30-percent-for/ | archivedate = 2012-11-20 | url = http://www.politifact.com/truth-o-meter/statements/2011/aug/23/thaddeus-mccotter/thaddeus-mccotter-says-lenders-lose-30-percent-for/ | title = Thaddeus McCotter says lenders lose 30 percent on foreclosures | date = 2011-08-23 | work = Tampa Bay Times | accessdate = 2015-03-01 }}</ref>。8月19日，他在新罕布什尔州做宣传，还参与当地电视台{{lang|en|[[WMUR-TV|WMUR-TV]]}}的《对话候选人》（{{lang|en|''Conversation with the Candidate''}}）节目摄制。次日，他与莎拉·伊丽莎白·卡普一起出席该州东南部（包括[[罗京安县_(新罕布什尔州)|罗京安县]]东部和[[斯特拉佛县|斯特拉佛县]]南部）的青年共和党人聚会<ref name="nh">{{cite web | url = http://www.p2012.org/chrnnewh/nhmccottervisits.html | title = Visits to New Hampshire by Rep. Thaddeus McCotter | work = Democracy in Action | publisher = Eric M. Appleman | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120612001650/http://www.p2012.org/chrnnewh/nhmccottervisits.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archivedate = 2012-06-12 }}</ref>。8月24至27日，他回到爱荷华州，完成竞选活动的最后一站<ref name="ia">{{cite web | url = http://www.p2012.org/chrniowa/iamccottervisits.html | title = Visits to Iowa by Rep. Thaddeus McCotter | work = Democracy in Action | publisher = Eric M. Appleman | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120612001356/http://www.p2012.org/chrniowa/iamccottervisits.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-06-12 }}</ref>。这个月底，麦科特尔现身《[[丹尼斯·米勒|丹尼斯·米勒秀]]》（{{lang|en|''Dennis Miller Show''}}），并谈及自己被排除在辩论以外的情况<ref name="mlive" />。9月7日和12日，{{lang|en|[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]}}和{{lang|en|[[CNN|CNN]]}}都举办了总统候选人辩论，但麦科特尔均未达到参与的最低要求<ref name="usa">{{cite news | url = http://content.usatoday.com/communities/onpolitics/post/2011/09/gop-presidential-debate-missing-candidates-/1#.T17rbIFTCAg | title = Three White House candidates didn't make cut for GOP debate | last = Camia | first = Catalina | date = 2011-09-07 | work = USA Today | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archivedate = 2013-09-19 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130919140826/http://content.usatoday.com/communities/onpolitics/post/2011/09/gop-presidential-debate-missing-candidates-/1#.T17rbIFTCAg }}</ref>。候选人必须在民意调查中取得至少4%的支持才有资格参加{{lang|en|MSNBC}}）的辩论。麦科特尔声称，虽然他没有达到这一标准，但在[[昆尼皮亚克大学民意调查中心|昆尼皮亚克大学民意调查]]中与他支持率相同的里克·桑托勒姆和[[洪博培|洪博培]]两人却都获得了参与资格。<ref name="mlive">{{cite news | title = Thaddeus McCotter says he's been shut out of MSNBC presidential debate too | last = Oosting | first = Jonathan | date = 2011-08-31 | publisher = Booth Newspapers | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archivedate = 2014-09-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140924200334/http://www.mlive.com/politics/index.ssf/2011/08/thaddeus_mccotter_says_hes_bee.html | url = http://www.mlive.com/politics/index.ssf/2011/08/thaddeus_mccotter_says_hes_bee.html }}</ref>。此外，加里·约翰逊和[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]]前州长[[巴迪·罗默尔|巴迪·罗默尔]]（{{lang|en|Buddy Roemer}}）都像麦科特尔一样，由于支持率太低而没有资格参加任何电视辩论<ref name="usa" />。

9月，麦科特尔仍在继续努力，希望能参与辩论。他在接受《每日来电》采访时称，别的候选人连“经济到底有什么问题都不明白，更遑论解决问题了”<ref name="bolton">{{cite news | title = GOP presidential candidate Thaddeus McCotter on why he should be allowed to debate | last = Pappas | first = Alex | date = 2011-09-09 | work = The Daily Caller | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140906223115/http://dailycaller.com/2011/09/09/gop-presidential-candidate-thaddeus-mccotter-on-why-he-should-be-allowed-to-debate/ | archivedate = 2014-09-06 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | url = http://dailycaller.com/2011/09/09/gop-presidential-candidate-thaddeus-mccotter-on-why-he-should-be-allowed-to-debate/ }}</ref>，他还认为外交政策领域也没有得到足够探讨。麦科特尔指出，自前任[[美国常驻联合国代表列表|美国常驻联合国大使]][[约翰·博尔顿|约翰·博尔顿]]宣布无意竞选总统后，外交政策的讨论就处于停滞状态。他希望下任总统会任命博尔顿出任[[美国国务卿|国务卿]]。<ref name="bolton"/>

9月9日，麦科特尔最后一次前往新罕布什尔州竞选，并在出地出席了两天活动<ref name="nh" />。他原计划要在5天后前往爱荷华州，但因需返回国会投票而被迫取消<ref name="ia" />。他在首都期间提出由[[格罗弗·诺奎斯特|格罗弗·诺奎斯特]]（{{lang|en|Grover Norquist}}）支持的[[社会保障|社会保障]][[美国社保辩论|改革]]法案，其中要求对50岁以下公民建立私人账户，并向他们提供一定程度的政府福利。他还呼吁其他共和党总统候选人公布各自的社会保障方案<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.slate.com/blogs/weigel/2011/09/12/mccotter_here_s_my_social_security_plan_now_show_me_yours.html | title = McCotter: Here's My Social Security Plan, Now Show Me Yours | last = Weigel | first = David | date = 2011-09-12 | work = Slate | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archivedate = 2014-09-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140906223115/http://dailycaller.com/2011/09/09/gop-presidential-candidate-thaddeus-mccotter-on-why-he-should-be-allowed-to-debate/ }}</ref>。此后不久，麦科特尔出席加利福尼亚州共和党大会，并在会上发表演说批评总统奥巴马：“无论他的竞选活宝轿车穿越美国多少次，我们都知道人类历史上最繁荣、最公平的经济是由你们、由美国人民创造的，而不是华盛顿的那群官僚”<ref name="la1">{{cite news | archivedate = 2014-09-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140902212035/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/washington/2011/09/gop-candidate-rep-thaddeus-mccotter-makes-his-case-in-la-ron-paul-tea-party-rally-social-security.html | title = Who is Thaddeus McCotter and why care? | last = Malcolm | first = Andrew | date = 2011-09-19 | work = Los Angeles Times | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | deadurl = no | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/washington/2011/09/gop-candidate-rep-thaddeus-mccotter-makes-his-case-in-la-ron-paul-tea-party-rally-social-security.html }}</ref>。但即使是在这次大会的民意调查中，他的得票率仍然不足1%<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.newsmax.com/InsideCover/Ron-Paul-California-straw/2011/09/18/id/411372/ | title = Ron Paul Wins GOP Calif. Straw Poll; Perry Second | date = 2011-09-18 | work = Newsmax | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130916090719/http://www.newsmax.com/InsideCover/Ron-Paul-California-straw/2011/09/18/id/411372 | archivedate = 2013-09-16 }}</ref>。麦科特尔还试图参加9月22日福克斯新闻频道举行的辩论，但他之后通过{{lang|en|Twitter}}）表示：“福克斯新闻已经亲切地告知，我不能参加在奥兰多举行的共和党美国总统候选人辩论”<ref name="la1" />。

=== 退出 ===
2011年9月22日，麦科特尔告知《[[底特律新闻报|底特律新闻报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Detroit News''}}）自己会退出竞选，称退出主要是因为无法参与总统辩论，“如果他们不让你参加辩论，你就无法参与对话，进而无法竞选”，“一定程度上是死于媒体之手。”<ref name="dn">{{cite news | title = McCotter drops long shot bid for GOP presidential nomination | last = Shepardson | first = David | author2 = Marisa Schultz | date = 2011-09-22 | work = The Detroit News}}</ref>。接下来他发布声明，表示支持米特·罗姆尼出任总统，并呼吁共和党人团结在罗姆尼身后，他也是最有望获胜的候选人。麦科特尔还在新闻发布会上称，他有意在自己的国会选区竞选连任。<ref>{{cite press release | archivedate = 2014-07-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140716064108/http://www.p2012.org/mccotter/mccotter092211st.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.p2012.org/mccotter/mccotter092211st.html | title = Rep. Thaddeus McCotter Withdraws His Candidacy (Press Release) | date = 2011-09-22 | work = Democracy in Action | publisher = Eric M. Appleman | accessdate = 2015-03-01 }}</ref>

《洛杉矶时报》在报道麦科特尔退出的消息时这样写道：“什么？你没听说过撒迪厄斯·麦科特尔？好吧，这正是他如今只是前候选人的主要原因。”<ref name="lat-wd" />《密歇根州政治内幕》（{{lang|en|''Inside Michigan Politics''}}）主编比尔·巴伦格（{{lang|en|Bill Ballenger}}）表示，麦科特尔“和竞选总统实在扯不上边。如果你想要有任何政治前途，趁现在支持米特·罗姆尼才是明智之举。”麦科特尔的邻居，前密歇根州部检察长[[迈克·考克斯|迈克·考克斯]]（{{lang|en|Mike Cox}}）表示：“他尝试过了，显然行不通。所以他现在退出，做出明智的选择。”<ref name="dn" />[[史蒂夫·科纳基|史蒂夫·科纳基]]（{{lang|en|Steve Kornacki}}）在[[沙龙_(网站)|沙龙]]（{{lang|en|Salon}}）网站上总结认为，整场竞选活动就像是个“警世故事”，“一位毫不起眼的国会议员在有线新闻节目中有了些许知名度，然后就自信满满地以为自己在全国范围内都有大批拥护者。”<ref name="salon">{{cite web | title = The sad story of Thaddeus McCotter | last = Kornacki | first = Steve | date = 2012-05-29 | work = Salon | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archivedate = 2015-01-20 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150120014448/http://www.salon.com/2012/05/29/the_sad_story_of_thaddeus_mccotter/ | url = http://www.salon.com/2012/05/29/the_sad_story_of_thaddeus_mccotter/ }}</ref>

== 余波 ==
退出竞选数天后，《底特律新闻报》采访麦科特尔，询问他对竞选时期的感受，对此他回答：“不，那并不是我生命中最糟糕的15分钟”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://politicalwire.com/archives/2011/09/24/bonus_quote_of_the_day.html |title=Bonus Quote of the Day |date=2011-09-24 |work=Political Wire |accessdate=2012-09-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120912000932/http://politicalwire.com/archives/2011/09/24/bonus_quote_of_the_day.html |archivedate=2012-09-12 }}</ref>。麦科特尔竞选3个月间的筹资情况于2011年10月上报联邦选举委员会。他一共筹得54万8606美元，其中46万8561美元是由获许的多家委员会转账，这些钱一共支付了54万1532美元开销，并且之前还有10万5367美元债务<ref>{{cite web |format=PDF |url=http://images.nictusa.com/pdf/912/12950305912/12950305912.pdf#navpanes=0 |title=October Quarterly (McCotter2012) (Amended) |date=2012-01-31 |publisher=Federal Election Commission |accessdate=2015-03-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223839/http://images.nictusa.com/pdf/912/12950305912/12950305912.pdf#navpanes=0 |archivedate=2016-03-03 }}</ref>。截至2013年6月，他还欠下10万5636美元债务未能还清<ref>{{cite web |url=http://images.nictusa.com/pdf/736/13963179736/13963179736.pdf#navpanes=0 |title=July Quarterly (McCotter2012) |date=2013-07-01 |publisher=Federal Election Commission |accessdate=2015-03-01 |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303221347/http://images.nictusa.com/pdf/736/13963179736/13963179736.pdf#navpanes=0 |archivedate=2016-03-03 }}</ref>。

2012年2月，麦科特尔在[[2012年密歇根州美国总统选举|密歇根州初选]]前夕接受《[[GQ|GQ]]》杂志采访，表示担心共和党人低估了[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]]的实力，由于对[[制造业|制造业]]和华尔街救业政策的立场影响，共和党将很难赢得[[美国中西部|中西部]]的选举胜利。他还表示，虽然自己同罗姆尼在汽车行业救市政策上存在分歧，但罗姆尼仍然是最有希望排除万难取得胜利的候选人。<ref>{{cite web | title = Primary Day in Michigan: Thad McCotter Is Worried His State Is Still Obama Country | last = Cogan | first = Marin | date = 2012-02-28 | work = GQ | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150301095127/http://www.gq.com/news-politics/blogs/death-race/2012/02/primary-day-in-michigan-thad-mccotter-is-worried-his-state-is-still-obama-country.html | archivedate = 2015-03-01 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.gq.com/news-politics/blogs/death-race/2012/02/primary-day-in-michigan-thad-mccotter-is-worried-his-state-is-still-obama-country.html }}</ref>

麦科特尔决定在自己所属国会选区竞选连任，但由于大部分支持者的请愿存在欺诈，他未能获得选区内共和党初选的入围资格，密歇根州总检察长对此展开调查<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2015-01-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150102002224/http://detroit.cbslocal.com/2012/05/29/mccotter-campaign-investigated-for-election-fraud/ | url = http://detroit.cbslocal.com/2012/05/29/mccotter-campaign-investigated-for-election-fraud/ | title = McCotter Campaign Investigated For Election Fraud | date = 2012-05-29 | publisher = WWJ-TV | accessdate = 2015-03-01 }}</ref>。麦科特尔认为，这其中肯定是“有人慌了或是在搞破坏……直觉告诉我，我们被信任的人欺骗了”<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.freep.com/article/20120529/NEWS15/120529029 | title = Only 244 of McCotter's 1,830 submitted signatures were valid; official calls it 'unprecedented' fraud | last = Gray | first = Kathleen | date = 2012-05-29 | work = Detroit Free Press | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150105123126/http://www.freep.com/article/20120529/NEWS15/120529029 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-01-05 | accessdate = 2015-03-01 }}</ref>。史蒂夫·科纳基认为，这些欺诈有可能和之前的总统竞选有关，因为那场竞选让议员无心顾及连任选举<ref name="salon" />，但麦科特尔驳斥这是“愚蠢的想法”<ref name="bb" />。他起初打算直接呼吁支持者把他的名字写到选票上，但最终还是决定放弃，因为自己无法在行使国会职责并配合调查工作的同时继续竞选<ref name="det" />。一个月后，麦科特尔从国会辞职，宣布这是配合调查的必要之举<ref>{{cite web | archivedate = 2012-09-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120912071737/http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2012/07/06/rep-mccotter-resigns-after-ballot-problems/ | url = http://www.foxnews.com/politics/2012/07/06/rep-mccotter-resigns-after-ballot-problems/ | title = GOP Rep. McCotter resigns, seat will remain open | date = 2012-07-07 | publisher = Fox News | accessdate = 2015-03-01 }}</ref>。随着调查的继续进行，调查人员发现除2012年外，有证据表明2006、2008和2010年麦科特尔的连任选民请愿书都存在欺诈情况<ref>{{cite news | title = More fake petitions for Thaddeus McCotter discovered | last = Gray | first = Kathleen | author2 = Joe Swickard | date = 2012-08-16 | work = Detroit Free Press | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archivedate = 2015-01-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150102003242/http://www.freep.com/article/20120816/NEWS01/308160222/More-fake-petitions-for-Thaddeus-McCotter-discovered | url = http://www.freep.com/article/20120816/NEWS01/308160222/More-fake-petitions-for-Thaddeus-McCotter-discovered | deadurl = no }}</ref>。为此，麦科特尔递交诉状，控告两名助手蓄意破坏<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/post-politics/wp/2013/04/12/ex-rep-thad-mccotter-suing-former-aides/ | title = Ex-Rep. Thad McCotter suing former aides | last = Blake | first = Aaron | date = 2013-04-12 | work = The Washington Post | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archive-date = 2015-05-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150513230451/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/post-politics/wp/2013/04/12/ex-rep-thad-mccotter-suing-former-aides/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。之后，他起诉的两名助手中有一人同另外三位助手一起受到与欺诈相关的罪名起诉，4人最终都被定罪<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.sourcenewspapers.com/articles/2013/07/30/news/doc51eef079ccf0d568848633.txt | title = Another McCotter aide sentenced in election scandal | last = Crumm | first = Charles | date = 2013-07-30 | publisher = Advisor & Source Newspapers | accessdate = 2015-03-01 | archive-date = 2016-04-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160402125958/http://www.sourcenewspapers.com/articles/2013/07/30/news/doc51eef079ccf0d568848633.txt | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《底特律新闻报》在麦科特尔从国会辞职前一天报道称，麦科特尔在退出总统选举后编写了一部[[电视试播|电视试播]]剧本，题为《保险杠贴纸：汽车城制造》（{{lang|en|''Bumper Sticker: Made On Motown''}}）。麦科特尔在剧本中成为综艺节目主持人，一众角色大多以他在国会任职时的助手为原型，这些助手会在节目中取笑麦科特尔的总统竞选经历，并探讨诸如性爱、种族和身体机能之类话题。<ref name="tv">{{cite news | title = TV pilot an outlet for Rep. McCotter | last = Schultz | first = Marisa | date = 2012-07-05 | work = The Detroit News}}</ref>莎拉·伊丽莎白·卡普也是剧本中的[[友情客串|客串]]人物，麦科特尔试图对卡普进行认真严肃的采访，但由于其他角色一直在说一些充满性暗示的露骨言论而未能成行，卡普也因此批评节目就像“火车失事”般混乱不堪<ref name="tv" />。这份剧本是由众议员的一位前雇员泄露给媒体的，以此来表明麦科特尔担任议员期间都做了些什么。对此麦科特尔否认自己存在任何不当行为，声称剧本中的绝大多数内容都是他在自己的车库中写的，为的只是要走去总统竞选失败的阴影。他还表示，剧本尚未完成，自己也没有授权发布，并且拒绝针对这一问题接受《底特律新闻报》采访。据麦科特尔所说，[[喜剧演员|喜剧演员]][[马丁·马尔|马丁·马尔]]（{{lang|en|Martin Mull}}）1977年昙花一现的节目《今夜费恩伍德》（{{lang|en|''Fernwood 2 Night''}}）是自己创作剧本的灵感来源，他本计划在2014年离开国会，并且还在为未来的职业生涯做准备。<ref name="tv" />

